videos.description: Kelly Bryant feels the pressure and throws it into the waiting hands of Tim Kidd-Glass to give NC State great field position.
videos.headline: Clemson turns it over on first possession

videos.description: Ryan Finley throws it deep to Kelvin Harmon, who is able to make the catch and stretch into the end zone for the 40-yard score.
videos.headline: NC State capitalizes on turnover with pass TD

videos.description: Ray-Ray McCloud uses his blazing speed and tight agility to maneuver through NC State and return the punt for a 77-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Tigers with first punt return TD since 2014

videos.description: Jaylen Samuels dives across the goal line and gives the Wolfpack the lead in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Samuels dives in for Wolfpack TD

videos.description: Kelly Bryant fakes the handoff and runs through the hole for the Clemson touchdown.
videos.headline: Bryant runs up the middle and dives in for TD

videos.description: Ryan Finley slings it to Jaylen Samuels on the goal line who dives in for the NC State touchdown.
videos.headline: Finley throws second TD of first half

videos.description: NC State head coach Dave Doeren says the second half is going to be the "best 30 minutes" of the Wolfpack's life and discusses icing Clemson's kicker right before the half.
videos.headline: Doeren talks about the successful icing of Clemson's kicker

videos.description: Clemson head coach Dabo Swinney says this championship atmosphere is thrilling and the Tigers will look for more stops on defense in the second half.
videos.headline: Swinney: 'This is what it's all about'

videos.description: Kelly Bryant lobs it up for Deon Cain in the end zone and  Cain is able to come down with the pass to give the Tigers the lead late in the 3rd quarter.
videos.headline: Clemson's Bryant hits Cain for late 3rd quarter TD

videos.description: Tavien Feaster capitalizes on a huge hole and then turns on the jets for the longest rushing touchdown for Clemson since 1993.
videos.headline: Clemson blows it open with 89-yard TD run

videos.description: Ryan Finley uses his third different target for his third touchdown pass, this time hitting Jakobi Meyers to get the Wolfpack to within 3.
videos.headline: NC State responds with another passing TD

videos.description: Ryan Finley throws his first errant pass of the game and Ryan Carter grabs the interception to start the Tigers inside the 30-yard line of the Wolfpack.
videos.headline: Clemson with INT for great field position

videos.description: Kelly Bryant keeps it and finds the corner of the end zone for his second rushing touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Tigers take advantage of INT with Bryant rushing TD

videos.description: One final chance for NC State on 4th and 15 and Ryan Finley's pass downfield sails a little too high and K'Von Wallace comes down with the interception to lock up the win for the Tigers.
videos.headline: INT seals the victory for Clemson

videos.description: Clemson head coach Dabo Swinney credits the Wolfpack for a good battle, but is proud of his team's resiliency forward to the rest of the season.
videos.headline: Swinney: 'Heck of a ball game'

videos.description: Joe Tessitore and Todd Blackledge discuss the fight from the Tigers and if they look like the championship team they were last year.
videos.headline: Clemson pulls out hard-fought victory against NC State

videos.description: Clemson quarterback Kelly Bryant throws for a touchdown and an interception and rushes for another score, while No. 20 NC State can't convert a long fourth down late in the game, solidifying the Tigers' 38-31 win.
videos.headline: Clemson survives test from NC State
